title: RussianEnglishTranslation
author: RussianEnglishTranslation
content: https://www.CandleLabs.org has a bounty program right now for bounty hunters and developers. Rewards go as high as 500k CNDL, which is priced at approximately .006 usd. There are live bounties for Candle Chain beta testers who follow social media accounts and who test their new AMM DEX. They also have grants for developers who deploy DApps or tokens on their chain.

comments.body: The bounty program is still open. The DEX is being tested now and I think the bridge to Ethereum will be tested next. They also have a grant program for developers and are hiring. Candlelabsdotorg

comments.author: RussianEnglishTranslation
comments.body: If you missed the first bounty, don't worry. The websites were just updated and the bounty button was moved. Go to CNDLchain.com or CandleLabs.org and click the beta testers button. Payouts are weekly and there is no KYC.
